Package com.aionemu.gameserver.network.loginserver.serverpackets

Class Summary
SM_ACCOUNT_AUTH In this packet Gameserver is asking if given account sessionKey is valid at Loginserver side.
SM_ACCOUNT_DISCONNECTED In this packet GameServer is informing LoginServer that some account is no longer on GameServer [ie was disconencted]
SM_ACCOUNT_LIST GameServer packet that sends list of logged in accounts
SM_ACCOUNT_RECONNECT_KEY This packet is sended by GameServer when player is requesting fast reconnect to login server.
SM_BAN The universal packet for account/IP bans
SM_GS_AUTH This is authentication packet that gs will send to login server for registration.
SM_LS_CONTROL
